[We must thank our Russian colleagues for reporting this outbreak with human cases in Ningxia Hui Autonomous Region of central China. As contaminated meat from privately butchered animals is at worst sold in a street market in the nearest next town, it is safe to assume that the human cases in the regional capital city of Yinchuan arose from another outbreak, and the awareness of the 1st encouraged reporting of the 2nd. There will now be others reported. As can be appreciated, China suffers from a universal under-reporting of this disease.

To find Sanhezhen, go to http://www.fallingrain.com/world/CH/21/Sanhe.html
To find Yinchuan, go to http://www.fallingrain.com/world/CH/21/Yinchuan.html
- Mod MHJ

